Earthbound Misc. Game Info--Money & EXP From Enemies. Site description: Lists the amount of experience and money you get from each enemy. A very useful guide.

Fan Game - Not to be confused with the Funfest Version, this is a new, full-length action game using a completely remade engine. It improves on it in every way, featuring more levels, bosses, enemies and playable characters, not to mention better controls and gameplay. Rescue the Runaway Five and help them save Venus before she is turned into a mindless zombie drone by Master Belch and his horde of music-hating undead
